{"tid":1713905,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【黎明之前】何不將鳩叫變成集結號令？","createTime":"2019-11-12T21:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T22:48:18.000Z","uid":53610,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"54d11abac3d523020e644fd932127be11931d955","tid":1713905,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T21:58:11.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得 黎明來到 之前依一句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最遠處吹來號角聲</span></span><br />\n號角的意義在於集結，集結民眾由最遠處的地方嚟到我哋的戰場，呼喚黎明<br />\n<br />\n一路以嚟鳩叫行動喺場抗爭中反反覆覆出現又消失，流行過一排但最終唔可以成為主流，我認為重點就在於場運動一直進步，但鳩叫行動就固步自封，一啲改變都冇<br />\n<br />\n隨著黎明行動的出現，我就諗，何不為鳩叫賦予新的意義呢？<br />\n<br />\n將鳩叫變成<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">集結號令</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺行動之前，樓上樓下都有手足準備出去之際，所有手足一齊大嗌口號，唱埋歌都仲得，叫醒訓緊覺的人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最重要的係</span><br />\n可以喺呢個時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">高呼行動時間同地點</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將成件事變成行動前的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大召集</span></span><br />\n<br />\n比如我係馬鞍山友，我就趁手足三三兩兩開始落到樓下嗰陣大聲鳩叫<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「六點半！」<br />\n「馬鞍山狗屋！」</span><br />\n再配合樓上樓下手足嗌口號和應，等成個屋邨的人都聽到行動訊息<br />\n<br />\n一嚟可以起到<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">集結號令</span></span>的作用<br />\n二嚟可以避免提前將行動訊息大肆張揚，可以將具體時間地點只喺小部分人之中流傳，到行動之前先通過鳩叫傳播具體細節<br />\n<br />\n唔好令鳩叫只係停留喺鳩叫，我哋要成為號角，去召集群眾，去呼喚黎明來到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鳩叫行動</span>要進化成<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">號角行動！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3f55f569b76d329a9467bf2bd2591e3530f7204c","tid":1713905,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T21:59:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n<br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n‼️Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n‼️‼️佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOhBMzzOW1qmypsfK5hxWA9U%3D&h=14a41aa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n‼️Sen Menendez 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOhBMzzOW1qmypsfK5hxWA9U%3D&h=9cbb576b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&h=6fdcee86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n‼️Sen Cotton 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sentomcotton/status/1194354865432092673?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsentomcotton%2Fstatus%2F1194354865432092673%3Fs%3D21&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOhBMzzOW1qmypsfK5hxWA9U%3D&h=71eef663\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsentomcotton%2Fstatus%2F1194354865432092673%3Fs%3D21&h=ac800806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sentomcotton/status/1194354865432092673?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n‼️眾議院多數黨領袖關注大學受襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LeaderHoyer/status/1194322000870854656?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLeaderHoyer%2Fstatus%2F1194322000870854656%3Fs%3D1